    "James W. Knox": "). How fitting then that the one they opposed is granted dominion over all forever. To the only wise God our Saviour, be . . . dominion. (\nv. 8). How fitting then that the one they opposed is granted dominion over all forever. To the only wise God our Saviour, be . . . dominion. ("
